@startuml
title Admin navigation

[*] --> AdminLogin

AdminLogin --> AdminDashboard : Login OK
AdminLogin --> AdminLogin : Login failed

AdminDashboard --> AdminDashboard : Filter by status (PENDING / ACCEPTED / REJECTED / ADJUSTED)
AdminDashboard --> OrderDetails : Open selected order

OrderDetails --> UpdateOrder : Set price and/or status
UpdateOrder --> OrderDetails : Validation error

UpdateOrder --> SaveChanges : Save to DB
SaveChanges --> SendPriceEmail : Send email to customer (new price/status)
SendPriceEmail --> AdminDashboard : Back to dashboard

AdminDashboard --> AdminLogin : Logout

@enduml
